title: Strawberry banana protein smoothie
ingredients: ['240ml almond milk', '1 chopped banana, frozen', '120g strawberries', '3 ice cubes', '1 scoop vanilla protein powder', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract', '1 teaspoon honey', '1 teaspoon milled flaxseed', '1 teaspoon chia seeds', '1/2 teaspoon ground cinnamon']
